  "description": "Built around filterEnvDepth at maximum — velocity sweeps the canopy spectral filter from dark moss to bright foliage. Soft touches produce low understory hum; hard hits crack the canopy open with light. The canopy cross-feed (xfCanopyEmerg) means high-velocity notes also trigger creature calls, making the emergent layer dynamically expressive.",
